componentDescription:
The top level Quick Filter component that provides context to child components.
It renders a `<div />` element.

className.description: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.

defaultExpanded.description: The default expanded state of the quick filter control.

expanded.description: The expanded state of the quick filter control.

formatter.description: Function responsible for formatting values of quick filter in a string when the model is modified

values.name: values
values.description: The new values passed to the quick filter model

string.name: string
string.description: The string to display in the text field

onExpandedChange.description: Callback function that is called when the quick filter input is expanded or collapsed.

expanded.name: expanded
expanded.description: The new expanded state of the quick filter control

parser.description: Function responsible for parsing text input in an array of independent values for quick filtering.

input.name: input
input.description: The value entered by the user

Array<any>.name: Array<any>
Array<any>.description: The array of value on which quick filter is applied

render.description: A function to customize rendering of the component.
